Author: tinuvhiel
Text: i am vegan so i already do that daily :-( these days have felt very different from my usual binges also because i don't like sit down and eat enormous portions of one specific food, i just have bigger meals with main, fruit, and sometimes dessert. it looks like normal eating but to me it feels like a bing and i need to tell myself to stop.
Usually some binges are associated with your body "asking" for nutrients. I've noticed that if I incorporate plenty of veggies and fruits into my daily diet, I dont binge and have zero urges.
